Package edu.ncsu.csc216.business.model.properties

Class HotelSuite

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.business.model.properties.RentalUnit
      • edu.ncsu.csc216.business.model.properties.HotelSuite
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<RentalUnit>
    public class HotelSuite
extends RentalUnit
    Hotel Suite to be rented. A child class of RentalUnit and is used by Lease. Overrides the following methods from RentalUnit: reserve, recordExistingLease, removeFromServiceStarting, getDescription, and check dates.
    Author:
    Kaitlyn Gosline, Sanjana Cheerla
